    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯的战时经济导致关键石油行业缺乏人力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/russia-s-war-mobilization-starves-its-crucial-oil-and-gas-industry-of-manpower</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯的石油和天然气工业对于为入侵乌克兰提供资金至关重要，为克里姆林宫提供了继续战斗的资金，即使冲突已经持续了第三年。但由于俄罗斯经济全面动员起来应对战争，加剧了长期存在的人口紧缩，该行业正面临着人力短缺的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/russia-s-war-mobilization-starves-its-crucial-oil-and-gas-industry-of-manpower</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴拿马选举领导人承诺恢复失去的经济繁荣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/panama-elects-new-leader-pledging-to-revive-economy-shut-migrant-trail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴拿马选出了最受投资者青睐的何塞·劳尔·穆利诺(Jose Raul Mulino)作为新任总统，他承诺重振曾经辉煌的经济、打击贩毒集团并关闭通往美国的移民路线，从而吸引了选民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/panama-elects-new-leader-pledging-to-revive-economy-shut-migrant-trail</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 01:50:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
